					</table>
					
					<div> <!-- NS4 Font Fix //-->
		
					Ross Fubini of Plumtree adds, "These vendors are working to provide an initial library of standards-based portlets, and will provide ongoing feedback, suggestions and best practices for successful JSR 168 and WSRP portlet development." <br> 
					</div>
